          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to perform a simple operation of retrieving a user's email based on their authenticated ID and then handling any potential errors that may occur during this process. It is part of the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ManualBill",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema and uses error handling mechanisms to manage exceptions. The procedure outputs a status code to indicate success or failure."
        }
